<p class="test-LocationInConferenceProceeding icon--meta-keyline"><span data-test="ConferenceAcronym">SEMANTiCS 2019</span>: <span class="BookTitle"><a href="/book/10.1007/978-3-030-33220-4" data-track="click" data-track-action="Book title" data-track-label="">Semantic Systems. The Power of AI and Knowledge Graphs</a></span><span class="page-numbers-info">
